        <summary type="html"><![CDATA[He was a menace.]]></summary>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>He was a menace.</p><p>We put him away for his own protection.</p><p>And also for yours.</p><p>We put him away where he can’t do you harm.</p><p>You see, we are looking after your interests.</p><p>We are interested in you.</p><p>When you leave, you’ll have no worries. We’ll see to everything. A good job on a good salary.</p><p>We always help our friends, don’t we?</p><div class="full-container"><iframe class="full-content" src="//player.bilibili.com/player.html?high_quality=1&amp;danmaku=0&amp;bvid=BV1Hy4y1V7BD&amp;page=1" scrolling="no" frameborder="no" width="100%" height="200px" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div>]]></content>
